high_descs: Walk across the room and turn right to walk down the passage to reach the dresser and turn left to reach the apple box.
Pick up the red apple from the box.
Turn right to reach the bathroom sink.
Put the red apple in the sink.
Turn around to reach the apple.
Pick up the green apple from the box.
Turn right to reach the bathroom sink.
Put the green apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the green and red Apple in the SinkBasin.

high_descs: Go ahead in this room to the circular table, then walk around it to the left to get to the two paths, taking the path on the right, then going straight until you can go left towards the apple on the floor.
Remove the apple from the right side of the box.
Turn right into the sink.
Place the red apple in the sink.
Go back to the box you got the red apple from.
Pick up a green apple.
Return to the bathroom sink.
Place the green apple into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place one red Apple and one green Apple into a SinkBasin.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the apple.
Take the apple from the box.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the apple into the sink.
Turn around and go near the apple.
Take the green apple from the box.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the apple into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Collect the Apple and placed it into the SinkBasin
